            <V n="text" t="single">
              <T n="single">0x98339C2<!--Today is a <b>Waxing Crescent Moon</b>, so here's what I can share with you, Kiddo:\n\nAh yes, the Baleful Bog! Did you know that the water there flows directly from the Netherworld itself? Yeah! It's what makes Mourningvale the Ghostly capital of the world. Botanists also speculate this is what makes the Undead Cowplants exist at all!\n\nYoung ones these days see a glowing puddle of supernatural waters with the power to alter their corporeal reality and say, "Cannon bomb!" oblivious to the dangers of having one too many <b>Out of Body Experiences</b>. I've tried to warn them about the possibility of impending <i>actual death</i> here, but all I get is an "Okay Doomer" response. Ah to be young and reckless.\n\nGhosts can find some interesting things here, too. If they've completed their <b>Soul's Journey</b>, they can take another shot at life and experience <b>Rebirth</b>.--></T>
